<bibRefCitation author="Rivas, L. R." box="[1170,1315,1707,1734]" pageId="22" pageNumber="323" pagination="579 - 611" refId="ref28867" refString="Rivas, L. R. (1986) Systematic review of the perciform fishes of the genus Centropomus. Copeia, 3, 579 - 611. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 1444940" type="journal article" year="1986">Rivas (1986)</bibRefCitation>
